OL,3,CReactions to proposed MLA salary hike
OL,4,C'understandable' ` First Minister
OL,6,FThe reaction to a proposed #14,000
OL,7,Fsalary hike for MLAs is
OL,8,F"understandable", First Minister
OL,9,FMichelle O'Neill has said.
OL,11,FThe Independent Remuneration Board has
OL,12,Fproposed an uplift in salaries for
OL,13,FMLAs from #53,000 to #67,200 per year
OL,14,F` a rise of 26.8%, from April 1.
