OL,4,C'understandable' ` First Minister
OL,6,FBoard chairman Alan Lowry said they
OL,7,Faim to ensure public money is spent
OL,8,Fwith accountability.
OL,10,FThe proposals are currently out to
OL,11,Fpublic consultation.
OL,13,FMLA salaries are lower than those
OL,14,Freceived by Members of the Scottish
OL,15,FParliament (#74,507), Assembly Members
OL,16,Fat the Welsh Assembly (#76,380), MPs
OL,17,F(#93,904) and Members of the Irish
OL,18,FParliament (117,113 euros/#102,369).
