OL,4,C'understandable' ` First Minister
OL,6,FAsked by media at Parliament Buildings
OL,7,Fon Friday about the proposals, Ms
OL,8,FO'Neill said she acknowledges there is
OL,9,Fa cost-of-living crisis.
OL,11,F"It is a recommendation that has been
OL,12,Fmade by an independent board in which
OL,13,Fwe have had no part to play in terms
OL,14,Fof any determination," she said.
