OL,3,CReactions to proposed MLA salary hike
OL,4,C'understandable' ` First Minister
OL,6,F"It's just been published in the last
OL,7,F24 hours, obviously we need to work
OL,8,Four way through the detail of it, but
OL,9,FI absolutely acknowledge there is a
OL,10,Fcost-of-living crisis, people are
OL,11,Fstruggling, people are feeling the
OL,12,Fpinch right now, so I think it is
OL,13,Funderstandable in terms of how people
OL,14,Fwould feel about it.
OL,16,F"But we will take our time to look at
OL,17,Fit, and we will respond to the
OL,18,Fconsultation in due course."
