OL,4,C'understandable' ` First Minister
OL,6,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,7,FPengelly added: "We will take time to
OL,8,Fgo through the recommendations in
OL,9,Fdetail.
OL,11,F"It was an independent pay body that
OL,12,Fassessed similar remuneration
OL,13,Fsituations elsewhere across the UK and
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,F"This is their recommendation, it is
OL,17,Fnow out to consultation, so we will
OL,18,Ftake at a look at that in detail and I
OL,19,Fhave no doubt we'll come back to this
OL,20,Fissue after the consultation has
OL,21,Fcompleted."
